<tr>
<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
Gabbie, a gnome in Solusek's Eye, drops the Molten Cloak as her rare loot, and the Mithril Quill is her common. Gabbie is a wizard so make sure you stun her and beat her down fast. There is also a Gnomebot in the same room that will attack as soon as Gabbie is hit, as well as another one that roams the hallways and will come to her aid if he is near.</td>
</tr>

